Three words, a little smile...

651
00:45:29,077 --> 00:45:30,912
You being you.

652
00:45:31,955 --> 00:45:33,373
Poor them.

653
00:45:33,415 --> 00:45:37,127
What if I don't only
have words to answer?

654
00:45:37,168 --> 00:45:39,421
