696
00:48:29,466 --> 00:48:30,800
Yes or no?

697
00:48:30,842 --> 00:48:33,345
No. I've moved.

698
00:48:34,220 --> 00:48:35,388
What?

699
00:48:36,056 --> 00:48:38,475
I still write there, dummy!

700
00:48:38,516 --> 00:48:41,144
